title: #92Noon! Grimm/Johnson/Birk
description: Gophers play by play announcer Mike Grimm joins PA & Nordo at the fair to discuss the Gophers' season opener tonight, Ron Johnson stops by the show to continue the football convo, & Matt Birk makes his weekly appearance!
